{"tid":1214322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[言論注意] 請立即檢討自己所有留言，警方/政府不停攞料中 [求置頂]","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:28:44.000Z","uid":176472,"like":355,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"c6e1acb08dde06aa42c5fe6a325ebdc6a1789838","tid":1214322,"uid":176472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:04:35.000Z","msg":"由不合作運動之所有留言，<br />\n到關於 612 期後的討論，<br />\n<br />\n1)請加上 純熟討論/利用 &quot;請不要&quot; &quot;我唔會&quot;等字眼<br />\n<br />\n2)切勿與三毛進行過激討論，浪費時間，警方會摘名<br />\n<br />\n3)所有 tg / group 要設期限 一日/三日 換 group剷人/剷 group，要求group 人全部 delete 內容，不希望 公海台主事件 再出現<br />\n<br />\n4)這是一個公開平台，所有人都會睇到你既留言/post 而警方/政府已有為數不少於五十人的小組不停碌連登摘名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">開心討論，利用文字技巧，勿與三毛辯論，合法地團結集合，再行動，別因為一時之氣做笨柒比人拉</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我愛連登， respect<br />\n老父做過警察公共關係科，休已退，<br />\n佢恨生左我呢個忤逆仔，但想教大家唔好亂瀨野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hi, 警察 uncle"},{"pid":"955197f7dea994320e91369af1299dd92de3141a","tid":1214322,"uid":132030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:05:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c6141da4e19aff994b785afc1a25dde9b46ea9b","tid":1214322,"uid":176472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:20:57.000Z","msg":"輕推推"},{"pid":"fca64f1068387533730a3edb8c34636b7fedbbc8","tid":1214322,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:23:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62d9b97f55d213e2a50844f5a229fc852df4a26e","tid":1214322,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b334e0091a17c7ad5bb6fbcf696452de4c46e10a","tid":1214322,"uid":166119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"84240c9725e56839091eabe436932e6424cc2ab6","tid":1214322,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04: